    <h1>About Project: Muses</h1>
    <p>
        The main purpose of Project: Muses is to provide a platform for sharing videos as tutorials under many categories, which are to be viewable to both visitors and members of the web site.
    </p>
    <p>
        These tutorials will be contributed by the members of the website and they are encouraged to structure their videos to be educational in nature. The tutorials must fall under ten categories when they are uploaded.  The users will also be able to add likes or dislikes and comments to the tutorials to provide better feedback to the other users.
    </p>
